project:
Controls:

- WASD to move
- Cockroach faces the direction of your cursor
- Left-click fires bullets
- Right-click fires lasers
- Spacebar to swap weapons between legs

Scoring:

- Your ego increases the more destruction you cause
- However, your ego decays over time
- The decay is accelerated for each time you are squashed
- The multiplier is also decreased for each time you get squashed
- Each marble/jawbreaker destroyed also grants a multiplier to future destruction

Mechanics:

- Marbles are destroyed by bullets but deflect lasers
- Jawbreakers are destroyed by lasers but deflect bullets
- Getting hit by a marble or jawbreaker stuns you, but doesn't kill you
- Deflected projectiles will persist for the remainder of the game, and are the only things that can kill you

Credits:
- All sprites done by Htoo Paing
- Background Music: Can Can - Jacques Offenbach
- Sound Effects obtained at www.zapsplat.com
- Shock sound effect exception at www.freesoundeffects.com
